p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: Adds a contains filter clause onto a query
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92: Adds a `contains` predicate to the given query. This predicate indicates to the query to filter out the objects whose the specified property does not contain the provided value.
The query to which the contains filter must be added
The property used by the filter to execute the predicate to check if that property contains the given value.
If true, take care of the case, otherwise apply the filter on lower case strings.
The value to which the property is compared. Check if the property contains that value.
